  <div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">Website under construction</div>
    <h1>Raid Ops in Web</h1>
    <p class="lead">Store your EPGP data online!</p>
    <p><a class="btn-primary btn-lg" href=<%= guilds_path %> >See all registered guilds.</a></p>
    <p><a class="btn-success btn-lg" href=<%= new_guild_path %> >Register your guild.</a></p>
    <p><a class="btn-info btn-lg" href="http://www.curse.com/ws-addons/wildstar/224405-raidops-epgp-loot-distribution-network-bidding" >Download in game addon.</a></p>
  </div>
  <div class="panel panel-primary">
    <div class="row" align="center">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h3>Upload data exported from addon.</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13pt">You will be able to keep it safe.</p>
        
        <h3>Keep your raid members updated!</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13pt">Anyone can check current EP and GP values , logs and items that dropped. </p>        

        <h3>Filter the roster!</h3>
        <p style="font-size:13pt">You can filter by class , role and minimum PR for example. Sort by all member's properties.  </p>
