    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <h2>Getting started:</h2>
      <p style="font-size:15pt" align="left">
          <li>Download game addon.</li>
          <li>Populate addon with some data.</li>
          <li>Go to addon settings and press 'Export/Import' button.</li>
          <li>Select the radio button with 'Website Export' label.</li>
          <li>Press 'Export/Import' button</li>
          <li>Copy the result from the box or copy directly to clipboard.</li>
          <li>Register <%= link_to 'new guild' , new_guild_path %>.</li>
          <li>Go to your guild's page and press upload data button.</li>
          <li>Paste the string and press Import button.</li>
          <li>Wait a few seconds and you are golden!</li>
      </p>
      


     </div>
